using a while statement and in interation variable and the len function we can construct a loop to LOOK AT EACH LETTER IN STRING

 fruit ='banana'
 index = 0
 while index < len(fruit) :
 	letter = fruit[index]
 	print(index, letter)
 	index = index + 1

